'''Irepuburika y’Uburundi''' ni igihugu kiri mu [[Bufirika]] bw’ubuseruko. Bukikujwe n'[[Urwanda]] mu buraruko; [[Tanzania]] mu buseruko hamwe n'Irepuburika iharanira idemokarasi ya kongo [[RDC]] mu burengero. Ikiyaga [[Tanganyika]] kiri mu burengero bw’[[Uburundi]] kiri hafi y’umurwa mukuru [[Bujumbura]] kikaba ari ica kabiri kw’isi gifise munsi kure cane.

* ''Izina ry’Igihugu'': Irepubulika y’Uburundi
* ''Umugwa mukuru'': Bujumbura
* ''Uburinganire'': Ibirometero kwadarato 27.830 (incuro indwi izinga rya Mayoroka)
* ''Abanyagihugu'': 7.020.000 (Icegeranyo c’igwiririrana ry’abantu mu Burundi muri 2003) mur’iyi myaka mirongo itatu iheze igitigiri c’abantu caraduze incuro kabiri
* ''Ukurundana'': Abantu 252,2 ku kirometero kwadarato: Uburundi buri mu bihugu bifise abantu benshi mu Bufirika
* ''Ukwikukira'': Kuwa mbere Mukakaro 1962

== Akahise ==
Abashakashatsi bavuga yuko Uburundi bwamyeho ka gihugu cikukiye kuva mu kinjana c'16. Mu mwaka w'1903 ni ho catakaza intahe y’ukwikukira igihe hashikiye abadagi;umwami w’ico gihe [[Mwezi Gisabo]] akaba yasinyanye na bo Umwumvikano w’i Kiganda. Haheze indwano y’isi yose ya mbere caciye kiba ubukoloni bw'igihugu c’ububiligi. Uburundi bwafatanijwe n’igihugu cu [[Rwanda]]: [[Rwanda-urundi]]. Kuwa 1 Mukakaro 1962 niho casubira kuronka intahe yaco y´ukwikukira irondewe n´umuganwa [[Louis Rwagasore|Rwagasore Louis]] umuhungu w'umwami Mwambutsa Bangiricenge akaba n'umukuru w’umugambwe w'abadasigana [[UPRONA]]. Uburundi cari igihugu cifashe kandi cagutse.Munyuma ku ntwaro ya babiligi gitakaza bugufi imwe mu ntara yari nini, ica yegukira Tanzaniya.

Akahise k’uburundi karanzwe n’igihe c’ubwami bwa kera bwabayehoimbere y’ubukoroni, n’imbibe zitahindutse. Uburundi bwashinze imizi kuva mukinjana ca 16 canke ca17 mu karere karimwo abantu kuva mukimpumbi ca mbere imbere y’umuzo wa Yesu kristo. Bwari Ubwami bushingiye kumigenzo n’amategeko kama y’Imana, umwe wese akamenya ico ajejwe ariko kandi ata migenderanire ishemeye n’amakungu iriho. Ico gihugu rero kitagira imihora co muri Afrika y’Ubuseruko, gitumbereye mukarere k’ibiyaga binini kikaba kigizwe n’[[abahutu]] (bangana n’ibice 85%), [[abatutsi]] (bangana n’ibice 14%) n’[[abatwa]] (bangana n’igice 1%) kikaba kirangwa n’imico imwe n’ururimi rumwe . Indimi zizwi kandi zikoreshwa mu kazi ni Ikirundi, igifaransa; igiswahili gikoreshwa mu buzima bwa misi yose.

Kuva Uburundi buronse ukwikukira, bwagize ingorane nyinshi zijanye n’ivyimibano na politike zagumye zigaruka arizo zatumye haba ingwano, haba abahungiye mu mahanga abandi bakegeranirizwa hagati mu gihugu, harasamburwa ibikorwa vy’iterambere n’ubutunzi. Ingwano yabaye mu Burundi mu 1993, niyo yabaye ndende cane kandi ni nayo yagize inkurikizi mbi cane kuvyerekeye politike. Kukaba nkako, uretse ihagarikwa ry’umuzo wa demokarasi, n’itituka ry’ivyerekana iterambere muvyerekeye ubutunzi ico kiza nyene c’intambara cateye, caranatumye haba itituka ry’ubutegetsi n’akaranga mubice vy’inshi vy’igihugu.

Kimwe mubituma indyane zidahera, n’igwirirana ry’abantu mu matongo yaze n’inkurikizi zaryo ku butunzi busanzwe bushimikiye cane cane ku burimyi. Abanegihugu bangana nimiriyoni umunani ugereranije bagwirirana ku rugero rugwijije na kabiri uko imyaka mirongo itatu iheze, bakagwira kurugero rungana n’ibice 3% ku mwaka. Tugereranije, dusanga hafi icakabiri c’abarundi bafise munsi y’imyaka 15, ibice bingana 90% babeshwaho n’uburimyi. Abangana n’ibice 70% nabo, usanga baronka agahembo kari munsi y’idorari rimwe ry’abanyamerika ku musi.

Inyuma y’ihagarikwa rya demokarasi mu 1993, ibihugu bigize kano karere (Ubuganda, Tanzaniya, Afrika y’epfo), bishigikiwe n’amakungu , vyarafashe ingingo yo kugarukana amahoro mu gihugu , ibiganiro vyatumye haba ishirwa ry’igikumu i Arusha ku maezerano y’amahoro n’uwumvikano mu Burundi. Amasezerano y’i Arusha ashimikiye ku mwumvikano n’ubumwe mu gihugu, agategekanya n’ingene abadasangiye ubwoko boserukirwa atamahinyu. Ishirwa mungiro ry’Amasezerano ryabaye intango y’intwaro y’infatakibanza, mu ntambwe yashitseko iyihambaye ikaba yabaye ishikirizwa muri Gitugutu umwaka wi 2001, ry’ibwirizwa shingiro rizogenga itunganywa ry’inzego mukiringo c’amezi 36.

Muri Ruhuhuma umwaka wi 2005, abarundi barahamagariwe kwemeza irindi bwirizwa shingiro biciye mu matora. Iryo bwirizwa shingiro risubirira iryamaze amezi 36, rirasigura neza ko Uburundi ari irepuburika yigenga, ifise na demokarasi kandi itisunga idini na rimwe , " yubahiriza ubudasa bw’amoko n’amadini ". Iryo bwirizwa shingiro rirubahiriza urugero amoko aserukirwa mu vya politique, mu nzego, mu buzi bwa leta, rikongera rikubahiriza intwaro ihuriyemwo abanyepolitike n’abajejwe umutekano mu gushinga urugero ahahutu n’abatutsi baserukirwako, badasize inyuma kwubahiriza uguserukirwa kw’abakenyezi kubice 30%.

== Ubutunzi ==
Uburundi n´igihugu gitunzwe cane cane n´uburimyi hamwe n´ubworozi. Ibice 90% vy´abarundi nico bakora. Kuva 1993 ah´ingwano itereye bifatanijwe n´ibihano bwafatiwe mu 1996 n´ibihugu bibanyi vyo kwugara imbibe; ubukene bwariyongereye cane. Ubu Uburundi buriko buratororokana kuva aho hasinyiwe amasezerano hagati yimigwi yahora igwanya ubutegetsi hamwe nigisoda ca leta. Abahinga babona ko uburundi bufise kazoza keza.

